Refactor Scope Lock:

When asked to fix/refactor something:
- Only touch files inside the target module path.
- If a change requires touching other modules, STOP and ask for confirmation (explain why).
- Prefer adapter pattern: create new function in module, keep old public API stable.
- Separate commits/PRs:
  1) pure refactor (no behavior change)
  2) behavior change (with tests)
